The opposite seems more straightforward:
```C++
if (IsIPv4()) {
    uint32_t a;
    memcpy(&a, m_addr.data(), sizeof(a));
    if (a == htonl(INADDR_ANY) || a == htonl(INADDR_NONE)) return false;
}
```
